# Contributing
Before making a contribution to SCIP, you'll need to agree to the terms outlined in the [Contributor License Agreement](CLA)

## Workflow
Please see the [wiki](https://wiki.zib.de/confluence/display/SCIPOPTSUITE/Development+Workflow) for information about our contribution workflow with git. If you don't have access to this page, request it from @bzfhende or @bzfmilte.

## Bug Reports
Use the following template in the Issue description to ensure consistency across bug reports.

```
commit: [<SHA>][/integer/scip/commit/<SHA>]
```

Ensure to always apply the ~bug label when using the above template.


